name: ImageDataTypes
shortdesc: Options for sending image data to the printer or file.

property.name: OPTIMIZED_SUBSAMPLING
property.shortdesc: Sends just enough data to print graphics at the best possible resolution for the output device.

property.name: PROXY_IMAGE_DATA
property.shortdesc: Sends screen-resolution versions (72 dpi) of placed bitmap images.

property.name: NONE
property.shortdesc: Prints graphics frames with crossbars in place of graphics.
